      *================================================================*
      * Procedure to link to CUSTCRE program to create customer record *
      *                                                                *
      *================================================================*
       CUST-CREATE SECTION.
       AD010.

           INITIALIZE UPDCUST-COMMAREA
           MOVE API-ADDR to COMM-ADDR
           move API-NAME to COMM-NAME
